<Link id="l00139" /><CodeLine lineNumber="139"></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00140" /><CodeLine lineNumber="140"><span class="doxyHighlight">  </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">// All logical elements added to the children, are sorted by any of the</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00141" /><CodeLine lineNumber="141"><span class="doxyHighlight">  </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">// following criterias: offset, name, line number, kind.</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00142" /><CodeLine lineNumber="142"><span class="doxyHighlight">  </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">// Do not add the line records to the children, as they represent the</span></CodeLine>

<Link id="l01086" /><CodeLine lineNumber="1086"><span class="doxyHighlight">  </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">// values encoded and assigned to the scope type.</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l01087" /><CodeLine lineNumber="1087"><span class="doxyHighlight">  </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">// Encode the array subrange entries as part of the name.</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l01088" /><CodeLine lineNumber="1088"><span class="doxyHighlight">  </span><span class="doxyHighlightKeywordFlow">if</span><span class="doxyHighlight"> (getIsArrayResolved())</span></CodeLine>

<Link id="l01096" /><CodeLine lineNumber="1096"><span class="doxyHighlight">  </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">//        DW&#95;AT&#95;type --&gt; ref&#95;type (type of object)</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l01097" /><CodeLine lineNumber="1097"><span class="doxyHighlight">  </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">//        DW&#95;AT&#95;count --&gt; value (number of elements in subrange)</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l01098" /><CodeLine lineNumber="1098"></CodeLine>
<Link id="l01099" /><CodeLine lineNumber="1099"><span class="doxyHighlight">  </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">// 2) DW&#95;TAG&#95;array&#95;type</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l01100" /><CodeLine lineNumber="1100"><span class="doxyHighlight">  </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">//      DW&#95;AT&#95;type --&gt; ref&#95;type</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l01101" /><CodeLine lineNumber="1101"><span class="doxyHighlight">  </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">//        DW&#95;TAG&#95;subrange&#95;type</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l01102" /><CodeLine lineNumber="1102"><span class="doxyHighlight">  </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">//          DW&#95;AT&#95;lower&#95;bound --&gt; value</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l01103" /><CodeLine lineNumber="1103"><span class="doxyHighlight">  </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">//          DW&#95;AT&#95;upper&#95;bound --&gt; value</span></CodeLine>

<Link id="l01108" /><CodeLine lineNumber="1108"></CodeLine>
